<div id="v490.24.7"><span class="G3004 s">Saying</span><span class="G5207 s"> G3754, The Son</span><span class="G444 s"> of man</span><span class="G1163 s"> must</span><span class="G3860 s"> be delivered</span><span class="G1519 s"> into</span><span class="G5495 s"> the hands</span><span class="G268 s"> of sinful</span><span class="G444 s"> men</span><span class="G2532 s">, and</span><span class="G4717 s"> be crucified</span><span class="G2532 s">, and</span><span class="G5154 s"> the third</span><span class="G2250 s"> day</span><span class="G450 s"> rise again</span>.</div>
