<div id="v490.24.20"><span class="G3704 s">And how</span><span class="G749 s"> G5037 the chief priests</span><span class="G2532 s"> and</span><span class="G2257 s"> our</span><span class="G758 s"> rulers</span><span class="G3860 s"> delivered</span><span class="G846 s"> him</span><span class="G1519 s"> to</span><span class="G2917 s"> be condemned</span><span class="G2288 s"> to death</span><span class="G2532 s">, and</span><span class="G4717 s"> have crucified</span><span class="G846 s"> him</span>.</div>
